  <?dbhtml filename="librsvg.html"?>

  <title>librsvg-&librsvg-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The librsvg package contains a library and a tool used to manipulate,
      convert and view Scalable Vector Graphic (SVG) images.
    </para>

